" a function to wrap around highlight
" allows you to set both gui and cterm colors concisely
function! s:hi(color_group, foreground, background, fontStyle)
    exec  "highlight"
                \ . " " . a:color_group
                \ . " " . a:foreground
                \ . " " . a:background
                \ . " " . a:fontStyle
endfunction

